    CLuaInstCCText::CCTextScroll: Add Parameter 'pages'
    
     - By pages parameter the number of pages can be specified
       to be scrolled
     - Set Lua api version to 1.30
    
    Example:
            ct = ctext.new{...}
            ...
            ct:scroll{dir="down", pages=2};

