svenhoefer <svenhoefer@svenhoefer.com>	2014-11-07

    - plugins: Fix assignment of prefered keys
    
    New keyword in plugin.cfg: key=<key>
    * key=red
    * key=green
    * key=yellow
    * key=blue
    * key=auto
    
    If entry is missing key is auto-assigned

