seife <seife@e54a6e83-5905-42d5-8d5c-058d10e6a962>	2010-01-16

    framebuffer: fix !USE_NEVIS_GXA case
    
    The GXA accelerator is a win for e.g. big boxes, but it is a net
    loss for the fontrenderer in the current implementation. So fix
    the framebuffer class, so that disabling USE_NEVIS_GXA works again
    for testing both cases.
    
    git-svn-id: file:///home/bas/coolstream_public_svn/THIRDPARTY/applications/neutrino-experimental@169 e54a6e83-5905-42d5-8d5c-058d10e6a962

